affixes.name: Fortified
affixes.description: Non-boss enemies have 20% more health and inflict up to 30% increased damage.

affixes.name: Bolstering
affixes.description: When any non-boss enemy dies, its death cry empowers nearby allies, temporarily increasing their maximum health by 15% and damage by 20%.

affixes.name: Quaking
affixes.description: Periodically, all players emit a shockwave, inflicting damage and interrupting nearby allies.

affixes.name: Encrypted
affixes.description: Enemies throughout the dungeon possess relics of the First Ones. Destroy the relics to summon the First Ones' Automa and gain powerful bonuses, based on the order in which they were destroyed.
